@startuml UC003_A1_Invalid_Directory_Input
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 20
skinparam maxmessagesize 60
skinparam sequenceParticipant underline

title UC003 - Floor Directory: Alternative Flow A1 - Invalid Directory Input

actor Administrator
boundary "resources/views/admin/floors/create.blade.php" as AdminFloorView
control "app/Http/Controllers/Admin/FloorController.php" as AdminFloorController
entity "app/Models/Floor.php" as FloorModel
database "floors" as FloorDB

Administrator -> AdminFloorView: POST /admin/floors (invalid data)
AdminFloorView -> AdminFloorController: store(Request $request)

AdminFloorController -> AdminFloorController: $request->validate([...])

alt Missing Required Fields
    AdminFloorController -> AdminFloorController: Validation fails: name required
else Invalid Image Format
    AdminFloorController -> AdminFloorController: Validation fails: image must be jpeg/png/jpg/gif
else Invalid Image Size
    AdminFloorController -> AdminFloorController: Validation fails: image max size 2048KB
else Invalid Data Type
    AdminFloorController -> AdminFloorController: Validation fails: sort_order must be integer
end

AdminFloorController --> AdminFloorView: ValidationException with field errors
AdminFloorView -> Administrator: Display form with error messages
Administrator -> AdminFloorView: Resubmit form with corrected data

@enduml
